###NOTES###

This setup file is for detector 1 of the HIREXSR diagnostic using
a PILATUS detector.  Bragg reflector is a perfect crystal with delta function
rocking curve.  Crystal/detector properties are the He-like crystal

**1/18/10** setting crystal/det properties 
**3/02/10** resetting ro,zo,gam,x0,x1,x2 based on z-focus/aligned CAD
**3/18/10** resetting ro,zo,beta,gam,x0,x1,x2 based on w-focused/CAD
            compared to laser alignment data
**3/19/10** x0,x1,x2 based on comparisons to w,z, ellipse fits

